 
- This tool is just something I am currently playing around with. It was written pretty shabbily a while back, and you can;t expect it to do much.
 I used to use it for testing and screwing around
- It is supposed to support intra - subnet peer discovery and file sharing
- This will later be extended beyond the subnet
- It has some minor diagnostic features built in, related to device media, etc
- It will shave your dog. 
 
 


